author: Engineezy
description:
Get the P2S from Bambu Lab here: https://tidd.ly/44aZyGe

Check out https://cnccutting.ca/ if you need some big custom panels made!

This is the Laser Cutter I use for all my projects:
https://www.xtool.com/?ref=rNX8YcbzlXsW8J&utm_medium=5306&utm_source=influencer

I have a bunch of cool mechanical 3d print files and merch available on my website:
https://engineezy.com

I also have a Patreon if you want to see some exclusive behind the scenes content: https://www.patreon.com/engineezy

Or Become an Engineezy Thangs Member and get access to 2+ premium files every month:  https://thangs.com/designer/engineezy
